[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1680","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1680.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0995","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 LSA 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Windows NT 4.0 本地安全机构子系统（LSA）中的 LsaLookupSids 函数存在输入验证漏洞。远程攻击者可向目标系统发送特制的畸形安全标识符（SID）请求参数，触发该函数处理异常，导致 LSASS 进程崩溃，造成系统拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 系统，无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 7.8，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0995"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-16T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:29.080","remediation":"立即升级至 Windows 2000 或更高版本操作系统（Windows NT 4.0 已于 2004 年终止支持，不再发布安全更新）。如暂时无法升级，可安装 MS00-006 安全公告中提供的补丁（KB249281），并在防火墙层面限制对 139/TCP 和 445/TCP 端口的未授权访问，同时禁用不需要的 LSASS 匿名 RPC 调用以降低攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ248185","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/875","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-057","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0995.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0995.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0995","https://github.com/edoardottt/missing-cve-nuclei-templates/blob/36c16d53eb6071e39cfc3cf88e99f1b340ec913b/data/year/1999.txt","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0995.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0995.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0995.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/1b2e09705f0816776a0a8a0cd6fc1208d25f09b2/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-m7p3-89hq-9rch/GHSA-m7p3-89hq-9rch.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0995.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1680.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1668","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1668.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0993","title":"Microsoft Exchange 5.5 ACLs 访问控制漏洞","description":"Microsoft Exchange 5.5 存在访问控制漏洞，管理员对访问控制列表（ACL）的修改不会立即生效，需等待目录存储缓存刷新后才能应用。在此期间，系统实际运行的访问控制规则与预期配置不一致，可能导致已被修改权限的用户在缓存刷新前仍可访问本应受限的资源。攻击者可利用此时间窗口绕过访问控制策略，获取未授权访问权限，影响系统机密性与完整性。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0993"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-13T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:28.833","remediation":"安装 Microsoft Exchange 5.5 Post-SP3 安全更新（即 Exchange 5.5 SP3 之后发布的累积安全修补程序）。临时缓解措施：修改 ACL 后手动重启 Microsoft Exchange Directory Service（DS），或在注册表中调低目录存储缓存刷新间隔（HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\\System\\CurrentControlSet\\Services\\MSExchangeDS\\Parameters\\Cache Refresh Interval（秒））以加速生效。根本解决建议升级至受支持的 Exchange 2016/2019 版本，Exchange 5.5 已停止支持多年，不推荐继续使用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0993","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/34851454a7b07498072de47d56f63daa4a4f524d/1999/CVE-1999-0993.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0993.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0993","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0993.json","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0993.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0993.md","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0993.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1668.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1609","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1609.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0992","title":"HP VirtualVault 未授权进程访问限制绕过漏洞","description":"HP VirtualVault 操作系统存在安全绕过漏洞。在安装了 PHSS_17692 补丁的环境中，未授权或低权限的本地进程可利用 Trusted Gateway Proxy (TGP) 组件绕过系统的访问控制限制，从而获取未授权的资源访问权限。该漏洞影响 HP VirtualVault 操作系统相关版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。厂商已发布补丁修复此问题。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0992"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"2000-01-18T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:28.707","remediation":"立即安装 HP 安全公告 HPSBUX9912-107 中指定的补丁（PHSS_18263 或更新版本），该补丁修复了 Trusted Gateway Proxy (TGP) 的访问控制绕过问题。在无法安装补丁的情况下，限制非授权用户对 TGP 服务的本地访问权限，审查并收紧 TGP 配置中的访问控制规则。由于 HP VirtualVault VVOS 已停止技术支持，建议迁移至受支持的安全操作系统平台。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www1.itrc.hp.com/service/cki/docDisplay.do?docId=HPSBUX9912-107","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0992.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0992","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0992.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0992.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/24ebb1752fdaa57c8d421b21085e47d359e1300e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0992.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0992.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x88000/87941/info.html","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--7e38d2e2-f104-4783-aa45-431b0eece3d7.json","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_idbypass"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1609.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1608","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1608.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0989","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5 DirectShow 缓冲区溢出远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 5 的 DirectShow 筛选器组件 MSDXM.OCX 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过 vnd.ms.radio 协议向用户浏览器发送特制 URI 请求触发该漏洞，导致任意代码执行。用户仅需访问恶意网页即可被利用，攻击门槛低。受影响的系统可在未打补丁的情况下被远程控制，危害严重。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0989"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-06T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:28.330","remediation":"升级到 Internet Explorer 6 或更高版本，该漏洞已在 IE 6 中修复。由于 IE 5 已停止支持且不再接收安全更新，建议升级到现代浏览器（如 Edge/Chrome/Firefox）。如无法升级，可在注册表中禁用 MSDXM.OCX 控件（regsvr32 /u msdxm.ocx）作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/861","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19665","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/c8abbfc77cc703e2fd85623576b0f07a0c8427eb/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0989.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0989","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0989.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0989.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/62aa382b460e7aee53e2fc9ebcfd565bebdac259/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0989.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/8954696320cbff8f7d95f98854cf0e72222fc646/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-564h-qm5m-jrhj/GHSA-564h-qm5m-jrhj.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0989.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153800_153900.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000922.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1608.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1608.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1600","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1600.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0987","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 安全策略绕过漏洞","description":"Windows NT 域认证机制存在安全缺陷，当域用户在登录时输入的域名末尾包含空格字符，系统无法正确下载并应用域安全策略，导致绕过身份认证。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 系列操作系统，攻击者只需拥有域账户，通过在域名后附加空格即可触发。利用方式简单，危害等级严重，CVSS 评分 10.0。微软已发布安全更新修复此问题。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0987"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-18T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:28.090","remediation":"建议立即升级 Windows NT 4.0 至 Service Pack 6a 或更高版本，该补丁（KB Q237923）修复了域登录时尾部空格导致策略下载失败的问题。对于无法升级的系统，应在登录流程入口处对域名字段做 Trim 处理，去除首尾空白字符，并确保域控制器和客户端统一校验域名格式。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ237923","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/3701042200a4e64b9e2a7f3614e9e958db6af9cd/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0987.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0987","https://github.com/aquasecurity/vuln-list-redhat/blob/ce91429859b5110820b1d31a41b0b1a3c67d9603/csaf-vex/1999/cve-1999-0987.json","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0987.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/62aa382b460e7aee53e2fc9ebcfd565bebdac259/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0987.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0987.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--1e5167f2-8c39-4729-bfeb-a8843e869244.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/fef2105ce9bc36a63673a5e0577e307a0953c8a8/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1600.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1520","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1520.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0985","title":"CGI City CC Whois 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"CGI City 公司开发的 CC Whois 程序中的 whois.cgi 脚本存在命令注入漏洞。远程攻击者可在域名查询参数中插入 shell 元字符（如分号、管道符等），当脚本将用户输入传递给系统 shell 执行 whois 查询时，恶意命令被一并执行，从而导致任意命令执行。该漏洞影响 CC Whois 1.0 版本，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0985"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-11-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:27.850","remediation":"立即停用或删除 whois.cgi 脚本，该程序已停止维护且存在命令注入漏洞。如确需 Whois 查询功能，更换为主动过滤 shell 特殊字符（如 | ; & ` $）的替代实现，或禁用 CGI 执行权限。在 Web 服务器层面限制 whois.cgi 的访问来源 IP 作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0985","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20433"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1520.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1508","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1508.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0974","title":"Sun Solaris snoop 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris 系统的 snoop 网络诊断工具中存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可向 rpc.rquotad 服务发送特制的 GETQUOTA 请求触发该漏洞，成功利用可在目标系统上以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Solaris 操作系统，危害等级严重，CVSS 评分 10.0。由于 snoop 默认以 root 权限运行且监听网络流量，攻击者可通过精心构造的 RPC 请求包实施远程利用。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0974"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-09T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:26.483","remediation":"立即安装 Sun 官方补丁：Solaris 2.5.1 安装 105403 补丁集，Solaris 2.6 安装 105404 补丁集，Solaris 7 安装 106996 补丁集。如无法立即打补丁，在 /etc/inetd.conf 中注释掉 rquotad 服务行并重启 inetd，或在防火墙上阻断对 RPC 端口映射服务（111/TCP,UDP）和 rquotad（3845/TCP,UDP,100002/RPC）的外部访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://sunsolve.sun.com/pub-cgi/retrieve.pl?doctype=coll&doc=secbull/190","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/864"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1508.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1506","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1506.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0973","title":"Sun Solaris snoop print_domain_name 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Solaris snoop 网络数据包分析工具中的 print_domain_name 函数存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。当 snoop 以详细模式（verbose mode）运行时，远程攻击者可向目标系统发送包含超长域名的特制网络数据包触发缓冲区溢出，成功利用此漏洞可导致以 root 权限执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.3 至 7.0 版本，危害等级严重。建议升级至受影响版本的补丁或禁用 snoop 的 setuid 权限以缓解风险。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0973"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-07T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:26.347","remediation":"立即升级 Solaris 至不受影响的版本（Solaris 8 及以上），或安装 Sun 官方补丁 106918-01（SPARC）/106919-01（x86）。临时缓解措施：移除 snoop 程序的 setuid root 权限（chmod u-s /usr/sbin/snoop），限制仅授权管理员使用 snoop 工具。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/858","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19663"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1506.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1500","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1500.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0953","title":"WWWBoard 2.0 远程密码泄露漏洞","description":"WWWBoard 2.0 存在安全配置缺陷，系统将加密后的用户密码以明文文件 passwd.txt 形式存储在 Web 根目录下，导致远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过直接访问该文件路径获取所有用户的密码哈希值。该漏洞影响 WWWBoard 2.0 版本，危害等级严重。攻击者获取密码哈希后可进行离线破解，进一步威胁系统安全。建议升级版本或限制敏感文件访问权限。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0953"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-16T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:23.863","remediation":"立即将 passwd.txt 移出 Web 可访问目录（如移至 www 根目录之外），并通过 .htaccess 或 Web 服务器配置禁止访问 *.txt 文件。建议停止使用已停止维护的 WWWBoard 2.0，迁移至支持安全密码存储的现代论坛系统，并对所有受影响用户强制重置密码。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0953","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/3065"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1500.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1500.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1500.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1409","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1409.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0951","title":"Omnicron OmniHTTPd CGI 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Omnicron OmniHTTPd 1.1 及 2.4 Pro 版本的 CGI 程序 imagemap.exe 存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的 HTTP 请求触发该漏洞，导致缓冲区溢出，从而在服务器上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响运行 OmniHTTPd 1.1 和 2.4 Pro 的系统，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。目前厂商已停止维护，建议迁移至其他 Web 服务器软件。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0951"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-22T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:23.620","remediation":"建议立即升级至 OmniHTTPd 3.0 及以上版本，该版本已移除存在缓冲区溢出漏洞的 imagemap.exe CGI 程序。如无法升级，应手动删除或移走 omnihttpd/cgi-bin/ 目录下的 imagemap.exe 文件，并改用其他成熟的 Web 服务器软件（如 Apache、Nginx）替代已停止维护的 OmniHTTPd。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/3380","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/739","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19566"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1409.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1406","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1406.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0944","title":"IBM WebSphere ikeyman 弱加密密码漏洞","description":"IBM WebSphere 2.0 与 3.0 版本的 ikeyman 工具使用弱加密算法存储 SSL 连接密钥数据库的访问密码，攻击者在获取密钥数据库文件后可通过破解弱加密口令获得敏感凭据，进而威胁 SSL 通信安全。该漏洞影响 IBM WebSphere 系列应用服务器，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。厂商至今未提供官方补丁，建议用户升级至不受影响的版本或采取其他访问控制措施加固系统。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0944"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:22.783","remediation":"升级到 IBM WebSphere Application Server 5.0 及以上版本，新版本已废弃 ikeyman 工具并改用 keytool 或管理控制台管理 SSL 证书，不再以弱加密存储密钥库密码。如无法升级，应将 key.kdb 等密钥库文件的访问权限限制为仅管理员可读，并通过操作系统文件加密或外部密钥管理服务（HSM）保护密钥库密码。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0944","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20274"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1406.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1400","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1400.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0943","title":"OpenLink Software OpenLink 3.2 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"OpenLink Software OpenLink 3.2 的 Web 配置器存在远程缓冲区溢出漏洞，未经身份认证的攻击者可通过向目标服务器发送特制的超长 GET 请求触发缓冲区溢出，导致远程代码执行或权限提升。该漏洞影响 OpenLink 3.2 版本，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重，成功利用可完全控制受影响系统。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0943"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-10-15T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:22.660","remediation":"建议升级至 OpenLink 4.0 及以上版本，该版本已修复 Web 配置器中对 GET 请求长度未做边界检查的问题。如无法升级，可在网络层通过防火墙限制对 Web 配置器端口（默认为 TCP 2611）的访问，仅允许受信任管理 IP 连接，同时在应用层实施输入长度校验，限制 GET 请求 URI 长度不超过 1024 字节。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/720","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19558"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1400.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1314","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1314.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0935","title":"Greg Matthews Classifieds.cgi 1.0 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Classifieds.cgi 1.0 存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者可通过在 CGI 表单的隐藏变量中插入恶意命令，导致任意命令执行。该漏洞影响 Greg Matthews 开发的 Classifieds.cgi 1.0 版本，由于程序未对隐藏变量参数进行充分过滤，攻击者无需身份认证即可构造特制的 HTTP 请求触发该漏洞，从而实现远程命令执行，完全控制目标服务器。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0935"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-12-15T05:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:21.687","remediation":"该软件已停止维护，无官方补丁。建议立即从 Web 服务器移除 classifieds.cgi 脚本，或替换为现代且受支持的分类广告系统（如 OsClass 或 WordPress 分类插件）。如无法立即移除，可将脚本所在目录添加至 Apache 的 Deny from all 规则或 Nginx 的 deny all 配置以禁用访问。同时检查 Web 服务器日志排查是否已被利用。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0935","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20442"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1314.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1314.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1314.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1309","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1309.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0926","title":"Apache HTTP Server MIME Header 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Apache HTTP Server 1.2.5 及 1.3.1 版本在处理大量 MIME 头部时存在拒绝服务漏洞。远程攻击者无需认证，通过向目标服务器发送包含大量 MIME 头部的特制 HTTP 请求，可耗尽服务器资源致其崩溃，无法响应正常请求。该漏洞利用简单，攻击门槛低，受影响版本包括 Apache 1.2.5/1.3.1 及 UnityMail 2.0。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0926"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:20.597","remediation":"升级至 Apache HTTP Server 1.3.2 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法立即升级，可在 httpd.conf 中通过 `LimitRequestFields` 指令限制请求头字段数量，减小 MIME 头泛滥导致拒绝服务的攻击面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://archives.neohapsis.com/archives/bugtraq/1998_3/0742.html","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/20272"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1309.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1306","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1306.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0918","title":"Microsoft Windows IGMP 报文处理拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows 95/98/NT 3.51/NT 4.0/2000 的 IGMP 协议实现存在输入验证缺陷（CWE-20），远程攻击者可向目标系统发送特制的分片 IGMP 数据包，触发协议栈解析异常，导致目标系统蓝屏崩溃或服务完全停止。该漏洞无需用户交互即可远程触发，影响所有受支持的 Windows 9x/NT 系列版本，攻击者只需发送少量畸形数据包即可造成拒绝服务。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.8,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0918"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-07-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:19.657","remediation":"Windows 95/98 用户请通过 Microsoft Windows Update 安装安全更新或下载 MS99-034 补丁（KB Q238329）；Windows NT 4.0 用户请安装 Service Pack 6a 及后续安全汇总。上述系统均已终止支持，建议升级至 Windows 10/11 或 Windows Server 2016 以上版本。临时缓解措施：在边界防火墙上禁用 IGMP 协议或过滤碎片化 IGMP 报文。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ238329","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/514","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-034","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19415"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1306.toml"}]